claim.claim-text:
A leakage detection device using a siphon principle, the leakage detection device comprising:
a water level measuring tube that has a closed lower end portion, and comprises a first inflow port through which leakage water flows;
a water collection tank that accommodates the water level measuring tube;
a discharging pipe that comprises a first inducing pipe vertically disposed in the water level measuring tube, a connecting pipe extended from an upper end portion of the first inducing pipe through a sidewall of the water level measuring tube, and a second inducing pipe extended from one end portion of the connecting pipe to a lower side of the water collection tank, a lower end portion of the second inducing pipe being disposed lower in position than a lower end portion of the first inducing pipe; and
a water level measurer that detects a level of the leakage water flowed into the water level measuring tube.
